projects.name: OLXmuj Website
projects.description: Created a customized online marketplace for the MUJ community. Developed a responsive website with user authentication, product listings, and messaging. Facilitated seamless goods exchange and enhanced university engagement.

projects.name: GymLog Website
projects.description: Created a web platform for university gym-goers to log exercise routines. Fostered fitness tracking and accountability within the university. Designed a user-friendly interface with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

projects.name: Predictive Maintenance for Jet Engines Using CatBoost
projects.description: Developed a CatBoost model that accurately predicted the Remaining Useful Life (RUL) of jet engines, achieving 67% accuracy with precision rates of 72%, 33%, and 95% across three health stages. Demonstrated the models robustness in handling categorical data, making it suitable for real-time predictive maintenance applications.
